                        <interp inst="t18430703-name-166" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS DEAN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 37.) I had the prisoner in custody for robbing a gentleman of a watch—he was tried for it—I swear he is the man.</p>
